Sentencas: The fracture energy at the interface between the porous cathode and the electrolyte of a planar solid oxide fuel cell is determined by a four-point bending test.
Titulo: Measurement of the fracture energy at the interface between porous cathode layer and electrolyte in planar solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: During the preparation of specimens the resin used to bond the stiffeners completely impregnates the porous cathode.
Titulo: Measurement of the fracture energy at the interface between porous cathode layer and electrolyte in planar solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The adhesion of the resin to the electrolyte is measured separately in order to extract a reliable value of the interface fracture energy (20.2 +/- 6.7 J m(-2)).
Titulo: Measurement of the fracture energy at the interface between porous cathode layer and electrolyte in planar solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The mode-mixity is found to be equal to 31 degrees.
Titulo: Measurement of the fracture energy at the interface between porous cathode layer and electrolyte in planar solid oxide fuel cells
